<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  {{> ../common/head }}
</head>
<body class="warranty">
  {{> ../common/header}}
  {{> ../partials/page-intro breadcrumbs=true}}
  {{> ../partials/image-content-block}}

  <section class="container">
    <div class="shadow-lg my-16 sm:my-20 p-8 sm:px-16 sm:py-16 lg:flex leading-6">
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-start lg:pr-4 mb-8 lg:mb-0">
        <h3 class="text-black font-medium mb-4">Warranty Policy</h3>
        <p class="text-base lg:max-w-65 mb-6">Please refer to Warranty Policy
          document</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" download="">Download</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-start lg:pr-4 mb-8 lg:mb-0">
        <h3 class="text-black font-medium mb-4">Warranty FAQs</h3>
        <p class="text-base lg:max-w-65 mb-6">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer aliquet, est eu convallis lacinia, ipsum augue mollis ligula, eget finibus libero odio non ipsum.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">See FAQs</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-start">
        <h3 class="text-black font-medium mb-4">Speak to a representative</h3>
        <p class="text-base lg:max-w-65 mb-6">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer aliquet, est eu convallis lacinia, ipsum augue mollis ligula, eget finibus libero odio non ipsum.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-100 py-16 sm:py-24  leading-6">
    <form action="#" class="max-w-screen-md px-4 mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-black md:text-center text-medium mb-6">Warranty Enquires & Claims</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-10 md:`text-center">
        For all warranty enquires and claims please fill out the form below for our review and assessment
      </p>

<!--      Claim type select-->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Claim Type</h5>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row text-gray-600">
          <div class="relative mr-16 mt-3 sm:mt-0">
            <input type="radio" id="claim-1" class="hidden" name="radio">
            <label for="claim-1" class="radio-label">Claim type 1</label>
          </div>
          <div class="relative mr-16 mt-3 sm:mt-0">
            <input type="radio" id="claim-2" class="hidden" name="radio">
            <label for="claim-2" class="radio-label">Claim type 2</label>
          </div>
          <div class="relative mr-16 mt-3 sm:mt-0">
            <input type="radio" id="claim-3" class="hidden" name="radio">
            <label for="claim-3" class="radio-label">Claim type 3</label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

<!--      Contact/Service-->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Contact/Service Provider</h5>
    <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="company-name">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="company-name">Company Name</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="company-name-1">
            <label class="input-label" for="company-name-1">Address</label>
          </div>
        </div>
    <!--        Row with 1 * 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label bg-white px-4 py-2 text-black focus:outline-none" type="text" id="City">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="City">City</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:flex md:w-1/2 md:pl-2">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pr-2 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="state">
              <label class="input-label" for="state">State</label>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pl-2 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="postcode">
              <label class="input-label" for="postcode">Postcode</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
          <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="contact-name">
          <label class="input-label mb-2" for="contact-name">Contact Name</label>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse mt-2 md:mt-0">
          <input class="input-for-label" type="tel" id="phone" pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{4}">
          <label class="input-label" for="phone">Phone</label>
        </div>
      </div>
    <!--        Row with 1-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="email" id="email">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="email">Email</label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

<!--      Location-->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Equipment Location (where equipment was servicesd or parts need to be delivered)</h5>
        <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="store-name">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="store-name">Store Name</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="address-2">
            <label class="input-label" for="address-2">Address</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 1 * 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse mb-5">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="City-1">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="City-1">City</label>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:flex md:w-1/2 md:pl-2">
            <div class="sm:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pr-2">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="state-1">
              <label class="input-label" for="state-1">State</label>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pl-2">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="postcode-1">
              <label class="input-label" for="postcode-1">Postcode</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="store-num">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="store-num">Store #</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="tel" id="Contact-1" pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{4}">
            <label class="input-label" for="Contact-1">Contact</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 1-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="email" id="email-1">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="email-1">Email</label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

<!--      Equipment Details -->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Equipment Details</h5>
        <!--        Row with 1 * 1/2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="Model">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="Model">Model</label>
          </div>
          <div class="flex md:w-1/2 md:pl-2">
            <div class="w-3/4 sm:w-1/2 mt-2 md:mt-0 flex flex-col-reverse pr-2">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="Seriel">
              <label class="input-label" for="Seriel">Seriel #1</label>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="clone-parent" data-clone-parent>
              <img src="images/symbols/plus-xs.svg" alt="#">
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="del-parent hidden" data-del-parent>
              <img src="images/symbols/plus-xs.svg" alt="#">
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 1 * 1/2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="manufacture-date">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="manufacture-date">Date of Manufacture</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:flex md:w-1/2 md:pl-2">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 mt-2 md:mt-0 flex flex-col-reverse pr-2">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="store-handover">
              <label class="input-label" for="store-handover">Store handover date</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
<!--      Description-->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Description <span class="font-normal">(Please provide specific details of the issue)</span></h5>
        <!--        Row with 1 * 1/2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="flex w-full flex-col-reverse">
            <textarea class="input-for-label resize-none" type="text" id="Description" rows="5"></textarea>
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="Description">Description: Please provide specific details of the issue</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <p class="text-tiny">Attach photo of issue</p>
            <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
              <p class="text-xxs">Maximum file size 5mb, File Type:</p>
              <span class="text-sm uppercase" id="file-type"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="drop-zone flex-center flex-col border-2 border-dashed border-gray-600 h-40">
            <p class="text-base text-center text-black">
              Drag & drop files to upload <br>
              <i class="text-xs">or</i>
            </p>
            <input class="hidden" type="file" id="atteched-file" name="file">
            <label class="text-xs btn-primary px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer" for="atteched-file">Choose File</label>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-end items-end mt-1">
            <p class="text-tiny">Attach photo of issue:</p>
            <span class="text-sm" id="file-name"></span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

<!--      Delivery Details-->
      <div class="mb-7">
        <h5 class="text-black mb-4">Delivery Details</h5>
        <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="address-3">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="address-3">Address</label>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="city-3">
            <label class="input-label" for="city-3">City</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 1 * 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:flex md:w-1/2 md:pr-2">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pr-2">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="state-2">
              <label class="input-label" for="state-2">State</label>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col-reverse md:pl-2 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="postcode-2">
              <label class="input-label" for="postcode-2">Postcode</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-2 flex flex-col-reverse mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="text" id="contact-name-2">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="contact-name-2">Contact Name</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--        Row with 2-->
        <div class="md:flex flex-wrap mb-5">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-2 flex flex-col-reverse">
            <input class="input-for-label" type="tel" id="phone-number">
            <label class="input-label mb-2" for="phone-number">Phone Number</label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

<!--      Terms-->
      <div class="border-t border-b border-gray-400 py-6 text-xs">
        <p class="">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed a magna purus. Vestibulum mattis urna vitae velit maximus accumsan. Fusce sit amet ipsum at quam mattis euismod ut non sem. Integer tempus magna a nisl congue, sit amet sodales sem porttitor. Nunc id dapibus lacus, nec lobortis diam. Ut egestas mollis maximus. Sed venenatis sollicitudin nibh a feugiat. Phasellus tempor ante neque. Fusce augue nulla, tempor sed gravida a, euismod ac orci. Nulla vulputate, sem vel accumsan bibendum, tellus felis fringilla eros, sit amet fringilla neque libero ac nisl. Donec pretium purus in arcu finibus, non fermentum eros sagittis. Fusce hendrerit vehicula ex, at dictum sapien interdum ut. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Donec eget ante enim. Nam eget turpis id mauris aliquam ullamcorper.
        </p>
        <input type="checkbox" class="hidden" id="terms" required>
        <label for="terms" class="terms-label">I have read & agree with the terms of service</label>
      </div>
      <div class="md:text-right mt-5">
        <button type="submit" class="btn-lg btn-primary">Send</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </section>

  {{> ../partials/cta}}
  {{> ../common/footer}}
</body>
</html>
